{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/model-plastik-raksasa-tokyo-border-break/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Model Plastik Robot Raksasa Akan Dibangun Di Tokyo","content":"<p>Apa kamu hobi merakit model plastik? Entah itu model plastik tank atau robot Gundam, biasanya model plastik ini dibuat dalam skala kecil seperti 1/200, 1/144, 1/100, dan sebagainya. Apa jadinya kalau ada model plastik robot yang dibuat dalam skala 1/1, alias ukuran aslinya?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48871\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48871\" data-attachment-id=\"48871\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/model-plastik-raksasa-tokyo-border-break/attachment/01-border-break/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-border-break.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-border-break\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-border-break-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-border-break.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48871\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-border-break.jpg\" alt=\"border break\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-border-break.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-border-break-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48871\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Inside Games</p></div>\n<p>Di Jepang, pengunjung stasiun KRL Shinjuku dibuat terkejut dengan kehadiran model plastik robot raksasa di lorong stasiun. Namun, model plastik ini ditampilkan dalam keadaan belum dirakit sepenuhnya. Pada dinding lorong stasiun tertempel beberapa <em>parts</em> model plastik tersebut yang masih menempel pada <em>runner</em>/rangka kemasan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48872\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48872\" data-attachment-id=\"48872\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/model-plastik-raksasa-tokyo-border-break/attachment/02-border-break/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-border-break.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-border-break\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-border-break-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-border-break.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48872\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-border-break.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Watch\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-border-break.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-border-break-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48872\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Watch</p></div>\n<p>Dilansir dari <a href=\"https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/1130633.html\">Game Watch</a>, Pajangan model plastik ini muncul sejak tanggal 1 Juli lalu, dan bakal terpasang hingga tanggal 8 Juli nanti. Tanggal 4 Juli besok, <em>parts</em> model plastik tersebut akan dipotong dari rangka-nya untuk dirakit menjadi robot raksasa.</p>\n<p>Melihat model kit robot ini, mungkin kamu akan teringat dengan robot raksasa lainnya yang jadi tujuan wisata di Tokyo. Ya, apalagi kalau bukan patung Gundam raksasa?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48873\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48873\" data-attachment-id=\"48873\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/model-plastik-raksasa-tokyo-border-break/attachment/03-border-break/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-border-break.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-border-break\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-border-break-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-border-break.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48873\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-border-break.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Ikidane Nippon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-border-break.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-border-break-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48873\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Ikidane Nippon</p></div>\n<p>Sudah sejak lama kawasan Odaiba “dilindungi” oleh patung Gundam raksasa setinggi belasan meter. Walaupun patung RX-78-2 Gundam tersebut sempat dibongkar, sejak tahun 2017 sudah ada patung Gundam baru, RX-0 Gundam Unicorn yang bisa berubah bentuk. Patung Gundam Unicorn ini juga sempat jadi <em>cameo</em> di film <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pacific-rim-uprising-film-super-robot-hollywood/\">Pacific Rim: Uprising</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48874\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48874\" data-attachment-id=\"48874\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/model-plastik-raksasa-tokyo-border-break/attachment/04-border-break/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-border-break.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-border-break\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-border-break-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-border-break.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48874\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-border-break.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Watch\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-border-break.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-border-break-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48874\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Watch</p></div>\n<p>Apa yang membedakan model plastik robot ini dengan patung Gundam tersebut adalah proses konstruksinya. Jika patung Gundam dibangun dengan konstruksi rumit menggunakan berbagai macam bahan dan material, maka model plastik robot ini kelihatannya akan dibangun sebagaimana model plastik Gundam dirakit. Bayangkan bermain Lego dengan balok-balok seukuran rumah!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48875\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48875\" data-attachment-id=\"48875\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/model-plastik-raksasa-tokyo-border-break/attachment/05-border-break/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-border-break.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-border-break\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-border-break-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-border-break.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48875\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-border-break.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Game Watch\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-border-break.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-border-break-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48875\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Game Watch</p></div>\n<p>Usut punya usut, ternyata model plastik robot ini dibuat oleh perusahaan game Sega dan perusahaan mainan Kotobukiya, untuk mempromosikan game Border Break untuk Playstation 4. Game <em>mecha</em> ini memungkinkan <em>gamer</em> memiloti robot yang bisa dimodifikasi dari penampilan sampai senjatanya. Dalam Border Break, <em>Gamer</em> membentuk tim dalam mode permainan PvP 10 lawan 10 yang sangat kompetitif.</p>\n<p>Penasaran kan, gimana model plastik robot raksasa ini bakal dirakit? Mari kita nantikan dalam beberapa hari ke depan! Sambil menunggu, kamu bisa melonton video <em>behind the scene</em> dari model plastik raksasa ini di video berikut ini.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HCzYuZ8PkF8\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"485643b0-6518-55d0-b4d0-3880ada109b8"}}}